what Max Siollun  in his classic "Soldiers Of Fortune" called "a government-in- waiting". I saw on Channels TV on Saturday an advertisement by the Chief of Army Staff, Lt Gen. Tukur Buratai on his proposed "empowerment programme for internally displaced persons". October 24, 2017 In "Candid Notes"